title: [FSX/FS9] FLYTAMPA - TAMPA REBOOTED V.2
description:
Features

Completely rebuild Tampa International (KTPA) airport scenery.
High Resolution surrounding Photo Scenery.
Hand placed Autogen with many custom landmarks.
Pre-rendered Self-Shadowing and custom reflection maps.
3D Taxiway bridge (FSX only).
Animated Cars & Monorails (FSX only).
Volumetric grass (FSX only).
Raymond James Stadium, International Plaza Mall, Sunhine Skyway bridge etc.
